{"tid":703281,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"[卡路B]成為我的奴隸吧!CONAN EXILES","createTime":"2018-06-15T15:11:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-15T16:42:40.000Z","uid":104422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"dc6039eda43fe889a33e8f6713c09061f752f320","tid":703281,"uid":104422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T15:11:23.000Z","msg":"2320開始<br />\n今晚直播到一點~會同其他朋友仔一齊捉小精靈(奴隸)<br />\n直播傳送門<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fIDaekYUoCY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DfIDaekYUoCY&d=VkgKX7psuiZEEb8vj76VhP1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=4b603a68\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fIDaekYUoCY</a><br />\n<br />\n　<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/15/230312_5d8cd4c0ec670c28f8d72aa05e2b1f40.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F15%2F230312_5d8cd4c0ec670c28f8d72aa05e2b1f40.jpg&h=be0a3873&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/15/230348_f3129457ddb50cf3cf2ef09b95c9a59d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F15%2F230348_f3129457ddb50cf3cf2ef09b95c9a59d.jpg&h=ebed70f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《科南的流亡》源自美國著名作家勞勃．歐文．霍華德的小說《Conan the Barbarian》，曾拍成電影《王者之劍》，由阿諾．史瓦辛格主演。遊戲中，玩家將將扮演流亡者，面對四面八方而來的敵人，以及席捲而來的沙塵暴，並要在這野蠻的世界中自謀生路。玩家要試著種植農作物或者去狩獵動物，並且建立庇護所，想辦法尋找資源來打造武器與工具。整個遊戲世界皆可以獨自探索，甚至與其他玩家合作建造整個村莊。"},{"pid":"cdd76e2000ab8c1968cea73b3b667efeb23b217e","tid":703281,"uid":104422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T16:42:40.000Z","msg":"HI"}]}